      <t>&lt;p&gt;This memo presents an elaboration of the SNMP administrative model set forth in [1].  This model provides a unified conceptual basis for administering SNMP protocol entities to support: authenticaiton and integrity, privacy, access control, and cooperation of protocol entities. [STANDARDS-TRACK]&lt;/p&gt;</t>
